ygData.messageBody:
Just to inform all kakis abt our SBS hunt in CB.

After killing more than 15 trainers, we only managed to get one SBS on the
13th trainer. The SBS is given to Einan, our only local kakis cleric. Due
to time constraint, we are unable to hunt for more. Furthermore, becoz of
the anti camp thingy that was implemented, the spawning of SBS are even
more rare.

Nevertheless I will con't to look for more SBS for local kakis like
Trifrost, Sereph and other tanks once I go back Faydark.

Tonight is Friday night, as per usual I will be training at NRo derv camp
next to mountain till morning. All kakis who wish to join me are most
welcome to do so.

Ziltus.
